race.description: Kennards Hire - Heat Of The Rising Star Hcp (Bm58)
race.comment: BURROWA (4) was a sharp improver second-up when chasing gamely to finish hot on the heels of JAK at the Sapphire Coast. Gets a nice pull at the weights with the 3kg claimer engaged, is peaking now and can go one better. STARLINK (3) continues to leave herself with plenty to do but is savaging the line. With weight relief from the 3kg claim she could be very hard to stop if close enough when straightening. EAST HARLEM (15) had excuses last start when slow to recover but his prior form stacks right up for this. Gets in well with the claim and has wet track form. Don't take lightly. NAVAL OFFICER (10) next best.
